OL,3,CWoman and young child die after
OL,4,Cgetting into 'difficulty' in water
OL,6,FA woman and her young child have died
OL,7,Fafter getting into "difficulty" in the
OL,8,Fwater at a west London park, police
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FPolice were called to Elthorne Park in
OL,12,FEaling just before 4.30pm on Saturday,
OL,13,Fwhere a woman and child were recovered
OL,14,Ffrom the water, the Metropolitan
OL,15,FPolice said.
OL,17,FLondon Ambulance Service and the
OL,18,FLondon Fire Brigade also attended the
OL,19,Fscene, where both people were
OL,20,Fpronounced dead.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@_O]
