OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777306271
OL,3,CWoman and young child die after
OL,4,Cgetting into 'difficulty' in water
OL,6,FIn a statement, police said an
OL,7,Finvestigation is underway, but their
OL,8,Fdeaths are not being treated as
OL,9,Fsuspicious. Police are now working to
OL,10,Fidentify the pair's next of kin.
OL,12,FDetective Superintendent Thackray
OL,13,Fsaid: "This is a tragic incident in
OL,14,Fwhich a woman and her young child have
OL,15,Flost their lives. Our thoughts are
OL,16,Fwith their loved ones.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
